        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="template-card">
        <p class="meta">Hero diagram · 1200 × 504</p>
        <h3>CPAC formula graphic</h3>
        <p>The bordered "stamp" rendering of the formula. Suitable for slide decks, article headers, embeds.</p>
        <p>
          <a class="btn" href="/assets/cpac-graphic.png" download>PNG (1200×504)</a>
          <a class="btn" href="/assets/cpac-graphic.svg" download style="margin-left: 0.4rem;">SVG</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="template-card">
        <p class="meta">Framework diagram · 720 × 660</p>
